short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Make the youtube player default to theater mode

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension forces the youtube player to always be in theater mode.

You can click on the extension icon to turn the feature on and off. 

The source code is available under the MIT License and can be found here: https://github.com/metasloth/youtubewhyd
